{"tid":873664,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"急！大埔尋貓😢","createTime":"2018-10-23T15:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T07:40:13.000Z","uid":40729,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4402eb70c6a74693fb9fd393417c8a76db5e3b0f","tid":873664,"uid":40729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"《急尋》<br />\n<br />\n姓名：Tata / 杏仁<br />\n顏色：黑白<br />\n身形：偏瘦<br />\n眼晴：黃色<br />\n貓齡：兩歲<br />\n性別：女孩<br />\n性格：乖巧、活潑<br />\n<br />\nTata在10月15號大埔頭華樂豪庭屋苑走失了，平時身子虛弱的Tata每天都要服藥增強身體機能，身為主人很擔心Tata在外面受不了天氣轉冷和風吹雨打，希望請各方朋友可以幫忙留意一下，萬分感謝。<br />\n<br />\n如有尋獲者定有報酬。請電：9263 4297(駱太)/9167 2960(駱小姐)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/230142_19515cd77526be8d288a9a8abc40d1cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F230142_19515cd77526be8d288a9a8abc40d1cd.png&h=cc5468a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/230153_2cbfc71d8c4b7e6b3d822204b1ec20f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F230153_2cbfc71d8c4b7e6b3d822204b1ec20f7.png&h=ad431c59&s={SIZE}\" />[img]"},{"pid":"3f5bc0be04bf275a4696992969c21f7e73fda540","tid":873664,"uid":137513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07f074c3e066a2ea55882885798b3db2d932a30b","tid":873664,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78513e074dc8999591df52c1af295a51ed85679d","tid":873664,"uid":40729,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"07f074c3e066a2ea55882885798b3db2d932a30b","tid":873664,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"本身住村屋。因為去旅行，放左係屋企入面，佢自己開門走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=